Layered Architecture

Layered Architecture

Dependency Inversion

public class Copy{
    void copy(File f, Printer p){
        while(!f.eof()){
            p.write(f.read());
    }
}
public class Copy{
    void copy(IReader r, IWriter w){
        while(!r.end()){
            w.write(r.read());
    }
}
